</script>    <div class="article-main-content">
        <div class="article-subtitle">
            <h3></h3>
        </div>

        <p>Smart Connected Chillers are reshaping how chiller service is delivered and improving results for connected customers. With more than 3,000 chillers now connected, more than 54 million data samples are generated daily. Chiller experts are able to access this data via dashboards and mobile apps, giving them a clear viewing into how the chillers are running, anytime, anywhere.</p>
<p>Putting this data in the hands of experts is producing real results for Smart Connected Chiller customers. They're seeing results like a 66% reduction in unplanned emergency repairs and a 65% reduction in the mean time to repair malfunctioning chillers.&nbsp;</p>
<p>These results are gaining recognition. Johnson Controls was recently recognized with a Microsoft Partner of the Year 2016 Finalist, Internet of Thing (IoT) Award.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="Microsoft IOT Finalist" src="/-/media/jci/be/united-states/specialty-pages/iot/microsoft-iot-logo.jpg?h=172&amp;w=300&amp;la=en&amp;hash=D8525F96F083AB52D49FE0FECF7F9B9C67353D2E" style="height: 172px; width: 300px;"></p>

        <div class="block-quote">
            
        </div>

        
    </div>

